PerlIDS (CGI::IDS)

Perl Website Intrusion Detection System (XSS, CSRF, SQLI, LFI etc.)

Version 1.0109 - based on and tested against the filter tests of 
PHPIDS http://php-ids.org rev. 1228

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc CGI::IDS

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CGI-IDS

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CGI-IDS

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CGI-IDS

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-IDS


